# Student Management System
[![Java](https://img.shields.io/badge/Language-Java-red)](https://www.java.com/)
## Overview
The **Student Management System** is a Java-based application to manage student records efficiently. It supports adding, viewing, updating, deleting, and searching student data.
## Features
- Add, view, update, delete student records
- Search students by name or roll number
- File-based storage (students.txt)
## Technology Stack
- Java
- File handling for data storage
- IDE: Eclipse / IntelliJ IDEA / NetBeans
## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/student-management-system.git
